\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula $[A*adj(A)]_{ij}=\stackrel[k=1]{n}{\sum}a_{ik}(adj(A))_{kj}=\stackrel[k=1]{n}{\sum}a_{ik}(-1)^{j+k}M_{jk}^{A}$
